com.quinsoft.zeidon.android

Interface ZeidonDisplayView

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ZeidonCheckBox, ZeidonDomainSpinner, ZeidonEditText, ZeidonEntitySpinner, ZeidonImageView, ZeidonListView, ZeidonTableLayout, ZeidonTextView, ZeidonViewGroup

    public interface ZeidonDisplayView
    A Zeidon android views that displays data is an output view and must implement this interface.
    Author:
    dgc

    • Method Detail

      • setFromOi

        void setFromOi()
        This is called from a parent ZeidonDisplayView to set data for the android view from data in an OI. If the view has child views then it is assumed that this call will also set the values for them..

      • getMappingView

        View getMappingView()
        Gets the Zeidon view assigned to map this android View. If this returns null then the mapping view is assumed to be the same as the named view.
